<i>noun</i>: 쟁기 <i>verb</i>: 갈다 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>쟁기</dt><br>
<dd>a farm tool having one or more heavy blades to break the soil and cut a furrow prior to sowing</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: plow, plough</dd><br>
</li>
<li>
<i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>갈다</dt><br>
<dd>to break and turn over earth especially with a plow</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: plow, turn, plough</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
